headline: Is Dollar Tree Stock a Buy, Hold or Sell at a P/E Multiple of 15.9X?
summary: DLTR's store and product expansion is promising, yet rising expenses and soft discretionary demand weigh on performance.

headline: Five Below (FIVE) Risks Market Expansion in a Cautious Retail Climate
summary: Specialty value retailer Five Below (FIVE) wants to expand its footprint while its competitors are backing off. The retailer intends to open 150 new stores in the current financial year. Recently, Five Below upped the ante in its first quarter and now expects to open 55 new stores compared to a prior guidance of 50.
